---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="A short note about me."
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		I build thoughtful web experiences, mostly with Astro and Tailwind.
		This space is where I publish notes on design, engineering, and craft.
	</p>

	<p>
		Right now I care about readable typography, calm interfaces, and fast sites.
		I believe the best digital products feel quiet, clear, and calmly responsive.
	</p>

	<p>
		If you want to say hi, reach out on GitHub or email. I’m more likely to reply
		to short, specific questions than long greetings.
	</p>
</Layout>
